OL,3,CMan arrested and two injured after
OL,4,Cstabbing outside primary school in
OL,5,CBirmingham
OL,7,FA man has been arrested after another
OL,8,Fman has been stabbed outside a primary
OL,9,Fschool in Alum Rock, in Birmingham.
OL,11,FOfficers were called to Bridge Road
OL,12,Fjust after at 12pm on Tuesday 3 March,
OL,13,Ffollowing reports another man had been
OL,14,Fseriously injured.
OL,16,FFirearms officers were deployed to the
OL,17,Fincident and several police cars could
OL,18,Fbe seen lined up in the street.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
