OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772579482
OL,3,CMan arrested and two injured after
OL,4,Cstabbing outside primary school in
OL,5,CBirmingham
OL,7,FA 32-year-old man has been arrested in
OL,8,Fconnection with the stabbing and is
OL,9,Fcurrently in police custody.
OL,11,FA woman also sustained injuries not
OL,12,Fbelieved to be life threatening or
OL,13,Fchanging.
OL,15,FDetective Superintendent James Munro
OL,16,Ffrom West Midlands Police, said: "We
OL,17,Fbelieve this to be a contained
OL,18,Fincident with a man in custody.
OL,26,@xD@bOU
