OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772579482
OL,3,CMan arrested and two injured after
OL,4,Cstabbing outside primary school in
OL,5,CBirmingham
OL,7,F"We are reviewing CCTV footage and
OL,8,Fspeaking to a number of people in the
OL,9,Farea. But would appeal to anyone who
OL,10,Fhas any information to get in touch.
OL,12,F"We understand how deeply distressing
OL,13,Fand concerning this incident is and we
OL,14,Fwill have extra officers in the area
OL,15,Fto offer reassurance to the community."
OL,17,FA public portal has been set-up for
OL,18,Fanyone who might have any footage
OL,19,Fincluding mobile phone and dash-cam.
OL,20,FYou can upload footage here
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@gO]
